<div><img title="Russia supports Pakistan’s stance on Afghanistan, drone attacks" src="http://www.nation.com.pk/digital_images/480/2012-10-04/russia-supports-pakistan-s-stance-on-afghanistan-drone-attacks-1349350963-3605.jpg" alt="Russia supports Pakistan’s stance on Afghanistan, drone attacks" /></div>
