					<p>
						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/russia-2/" rel="category tag">Russia</a></span>
						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/armenia-azerbaijan-conflict/" rel="tag">Armenia-Azerbaijan Conflict</a></span>					</p>
